Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on developing a visual tracking system for object detection and tracking in videos. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the proposed system can be used for robotic applications. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is another possible category as the paper deals with processing and analyzing video data. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper involves developing an intelligent fusion framework for tracking. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also possible as the paper involves using machine learning techniques for object detection and tracking.
